Open Codeanywhere
Create folder called Shopping Cart
Open PHPMyAdmin
Create table called tbl_product1 
The columns are as follows 
- id - int, auto increment, Index=primary
- name - varchar
- image - varchar 
- price - double

Insert 3 rows of sample data
In your project folder in Codeanywhere, create an image folder and upload 3 product images
Create a file called index.php
Create a file called success.php
